            {
              "content": "=\"Act as a Proper SERP Query Generator analyse the {{ $json.final_query }} and generate a propery search query as multiple to search in google to find company names return as only validjson do not include code markdowns or instructions\n\nAvoid generating queries which relates to linkedin\n\nEverything should be Recent on this Current year 2026"
